ECB’s Makuch Says Euro Area Needs to ’Complete Fiscal Pillar’

-- B y   R a d o s l a v   T o m e k
-- 
2011-10-13T08:39:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/ecb-s-makuch-says-euro-area-needs-to-complete-fiscal-pillar-.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member Jozef Makuch said the euro area needs to complete
its “fiscal pillar” to match that of monetary policy.  Makuch said the euro is based on one pillar -- common
monetary policy -- and needs a second one, the fiscal pillar.  Makuch, who also heads the National Bank of Slovakia, was
speaking at an event in Bratislava today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Radoslav Tomek in Bratislava at 
 rtomek@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeff Black at 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net  